.TH KINGPEPE-QT 1
.SH NAME
kingpepe-qt \- graphical KingPepe Core wallet and node
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B kingpepe-qt
[\fIOPTIONS\fR] [\fIURI\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
The
.B kingpepe-qt
application provides a graphical interface for running a KingPepe Core node,
managing wallets, and sending or receiving KingPepe transactions.
.SH OPTIONS
Run
.B kingpepe-qt -help
for the complete option list supported by this build.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR kingpeped (1),
.BR kingpepe-cli (1)
